<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../888/4112888.xml">
Stick It</link></movie>
</it> show his improvisational and comedic timing skills. Whereas roles in <it><movie wordnetid="106613686" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../467/12639467.xml">
The Boost</link></movie>
</it>, with <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../576/168576.xml">
James Woods</link></actor>
