<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../932/5549932.xml">
Internal Affairs</link></movie>
</it> with <actor wordnetid="109765278" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../956/153956.xml">
Richard Gere</link></actor>
, present his adaptability for dramatic roles.</p>
